Included patch to display Matroska container chapter names.

http://smplayer.berlios.de/forum/viewtopic.php?f=4&t=661

Patch by dikei for smplayer, modified, for umplayer.

Included patch - with GUI - to optionally enable VDPAU DivX/XviD decoding, when VDPAU is
the selected output, through an option in the smplayer.ini file as shown in:

http://smplayer.berlios.de/forum/viewtopic.php?f=4&t=285

By default, it is disabled.

